Package KioskApp.FrontEnd

package KioskApp.FrontEnd
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    BottomBarPanel
    A class that extends JPanel that is the UI for the bottom component seen in a few windows in KioskApp.
    CartPageCartPanel
    A class that extends JPanel that is the UI for the cart page's cart table.
    CartPageFrame
    A class that extends JFrame that is the frame for the cart page of KioskApp that puts the various components on the screen in the desired locations.
    LoginPanel
    A class that extends JPanel that has ActionListeners that represents the login interface with the functionality of allowing a user to login.
    LogoBarPanel
    A class that extends JPanel that is the UI for the logo that is seen in various windows in KioskApp.
    Main
    Class that starts the KioskApp program.
    MainFrame
    A class that extends JFrame that acts as a default frame for a few of the windows used in KioskApp.
    MainPagePanel
    A class that extends JPanel that is a UI for the default page located after logging in.
    NumberPanel
    A class that extends JPanel that is a UI for the number panel that is on KioskApp's cart page.
    PaymentTypePanel
    A class that extends JPanel that is a UI for the payments portion of KioskApp.
    ReceiptGenerator
    Class that generates receipts with the items added to the cart in the cart page, accessible from the payment page.
    SearchedItemsPanel
    A class that extends JPanel that acts as a UI for items that are searched for from TopBarPanel's searchbar which are in a table format.
    TopBarPanel
    A class that extends JPanel that is a UI for the search bar and request assistance button that is located below the logo on the cart page.
    TotalBarPanel
    A class that extends JPanel that is a UI that operates as a total panel.
